Span.Text: Ensure workers are kept safe utilising Microsoft Azure services and mobile applications delivered onto tablets, smart phones and more innovative devices like the Microsoft Band.

¬Simplify access to internal tools and resources such as training, routing schedules, and territory management by providing a consistent, connected and seamless experience across applications and devices for all personal preferences.

Increase operational safety by making safety and maintenance information available to all relevant people at any time, on any device, with the added ability to easily collaborate if there are any questions.

By providing remote, online access to all health & safety, operational and role-based training, field workers don't have to take time out to travel to static offices to do their training. Training schedules can be monitored and managed remotely ensuring all workers are kept up to date on their training whilst allowing workers flexibility in when or where they are trained.
